            <lg xml:id="TK696">
<l>kuṟippaṟintu kālaṅ karuti veṟuppila</l>
<l>vēṇṭupa vēṭpac colal</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Knowing the (king's disposition and seeking the right time, (the minister) should in a pleasing manner suggest things such as are desirable and not disagreeable.</l>
            </lg>
